    "description": "<strong><i>Minimal Slide</i></strong> is a sliding puzzle game rich of features and with puzzles for players of every skill level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/10a639a81d607992776d2d086450a799.poster.avif?t=1727975418\" width=610 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/10a639a81d607992776d2d086450a799.webm?t=1727975418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/10a639a81d607992776d2d086450a799.mp4?t=1727975418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/790cbfa52e13e3b7ae3566106d7b3804.webp?t=1727975418\" width=150 height=30 /></span><br><br>The game features <strong>over 100 levels</strong>, divided in three difficulties, using many different types of tiles from classic tetrominoes to more complex shapes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/1054793324091f64b5e5161cba421531.webp?t=1727975418\" width=150 height=31 /></span><br><br>Beating a level is not always the end of it: try to complete it with the least amount of moves to reach the <i>star score</i>. You'll need to come up with new strategies to succeed, uncovering the hidden depth of the game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/2f948bee7ac49648d958ed15769ed6d1.poster.avif?t=1727975418\" width=610 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/2f948bee7ac49648d958ed15769ed6d1.webm?t=1727975418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/2f948bee7ac49648d958ed15769ed6d1.mp4?t=1727975418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/8b567b442caac989de69b20b3aa69367.webp?t=1727975418\" width=150 height=30 /></span><br><br>The first time you beat a level, you earn coins you can use to unlock colors, textures and more with which you can <strong>customize</strong> the game's appearance. If you're lucky, you can even win rare special sets with unique visuals and sounds for the tiles!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/73348a2e00eccffc0f05abaa03a18570.webp?t=1727975418\" width=150 height=30 /></span><br><br>Can't decide how to customize the game? Use the <i>randomizer</i> to randomly change visuals and sounds. You can even choose to randomize any combination of them each time you start a level!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/b4b95e5950bef099fbe142a9a941609d.poster.avif?t=1727975418\" width=610 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/b4b95e5950bef099fbe142a9a941609d.webm?t=1727975418\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/b4b95e5950bef099fbe142a9a941609d.mp4?t=1727975418\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3163570/extras/76b2b73d87b2d079468fd3fcc623b5bc.webp?t=1727975418\" width=150 height=30 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 100 levels divided in three difficulties. </li><li>50+ customize options. </li><li>Randomizer for the game's appearance. </li><li>Various statistics about beaten levels. </li><li>Original soundtrack and sound effects.</li></ul>",
